<xml xmlns="https://developers.google.com/blockly/xml"><variables></variables><comment id="M$)/X3%r!vauHL+i#/aC" x="209" y="338" w="598" h="184">
On quadrant 1, display the text: "Quad 1", repeat for quadrants 2, 3, 4.

If your string is too long, "&gt;8 chars" will display instead of your text.
</comment><comment id="IcI8?Ofiikjw*Nfw9!Pq" x="28" y="206" w="163" h="226">Modify &amp; Create: If you press a button, move the message to a new quadrant.</comment><block type="pxt-on-start" id="P.#uBzuZH5o2,9pfXo]W" x="38" y="50"><statement name="HANDLER"><block type="fwd_lcd_initialize" id="9Xr?}onS${uBcmxVZtc3"></block></statement></block><block type="device_forever" id=";#p8rLk}HY={Jb0g)EH@" x="218" y="51"><data>{"commentRefs":["0"],"fieldData":{}}</data><statement name="HANDLER"><block type="fwd_lcd_print_quadrant_string" id="5]C5lq]*QweB7DUVT12*"><field name="this">fwdSensors.lcd1</field><value name="text"><shadow type="text" id="FjTBSpnb|==0sTJAoE#H"><field name="TEXT">Quad 1</field></shadow></value><value name="quadrant"><shadow type="math_number_minmax" id="s|xGtdPizyVJfSe}c$j5"><mutation min="1" max="4" label="Quadrant" precision="0"></mutation><field name="SLIDER">1</field></shadow></value><next><block type="fwd_lcd_print_quadrant_string" id="w{pN`9A0uafFj3me6m-i"><field name="this">fwdSensors.lcd1</field><value name="text"><shadow type="text" id="1d`{,;JK?72JLNk2!4~x"><field name="TEXT">Quad 2</field></shadow></value><value name="quadrant"><shadow type="math_number_minmax" id="aOlsqz9FB{.$=MppgnWT"><mutation min="1" max="4" label="Quadrant" precision="0"></mutation><field name="SLIDER">2</field></shadow></value><next><block type="fwd_lcd_print_quadrant_string" id="i$d6uZ(O~%Hi[mf;SM%7"><field name="this">fwdSensors.lcd1</field><value name="text"><shadow type="text" id="4![u+{JtYT_BY=-?S42u"><field name="TEXT">Quad 3</field></shadow></value><value name="quadrant"><shadow type="math_number_minmax" id="2_?BpJHO.fVpyHz}yi,Y"><mutation min="1" max="4" label="Quadrant" precision="0"></mutation><field name="SLIDER">3</field></shadow></value><next><block type="fwd_lcd_print_quadrant_string" id="2WB[w~z%GY*Xp#Odf~a0"><field name="this">fwdSensors.lcd1</field><value name="text"><shadow type="text" id="=^IdZo;b`0kP#r@5:MKQ"><field name="TEXT">Quad 4</field></shado